<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued December 17 at 4:02AM EST until December 18 at 1:00AM EST by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 1 AM EST
SUNDAY...
* WHAT...Lake effect snow. Additional snow accumulations of 2 to 4
inches. Gusty west-southwest winds up to around 20 to 25 mph at
times could lead to some blowing and drifting snow. Travel
could be hazardous.
* WHERE...Northern Berrien County.
* WHEN...Until 1 AM EST Sunday.
* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling.</instruction>
